under the BorderLayout manager’5 control. But anything inside the 
panel (in other words, components added to the panel by calling 
panel.add(aComponent)) are under the panel’5 FlowLayout 
manager’5 control. We’11 start by putting an empty panel in the frame’5 
east region, and on the next pages we’11 add things to the panel.
